    { "label": "lbrs-portal-z286",             "xyz": [-7531.0, -1226.0, 286.0], "settleToleranceY": 1.0, "note": "LBRS literal portal coord; validates the BRM upper-spire poly cluster (UBRS shares this cluster per the original fixture's note). Tested last because the LBRS area-trigger transitions the bot to instance 229 on `.go xyz`; the BRS-instance-load that follows would corrupt any subsequent waypoint." }
